PRECIOUS Okonkwo aka Precious P Money has announced his decision to start a new record label to further give up and coming talents opportunities. Okonkwo also announced that aside from establishing his record label, P Money records, he is also building an ultramodern studio to give up and coming talents opportunities. The music enthusiast and entrepreneur also revealed that plans are on the way to kick start a music reality TV show. In his words: “you don’t have to see or wait for opportunities to come when you can create them. This is one of the reasons we have introduced regular concerts where artistes can perform and get financial rewards from fans asides from their performance fees.” The Delta State-born entrepreneur who doubles as a tech executive also plans to create his distribution channel where his outfit can directly circulate music content from artists and monetize it without involving a third party.